@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rbuavx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.30) + v0))
    v2 = v1
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v2 + 0.69) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.70)))
    v1 = ((v2 - (tmp + 0.90 + v2 + 0.76)) - tmp)
    v2 = 0.19
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v0 + 0.41) / (v1 + 0.95 / v0 + 0.44)))
    tmp = (tmp / ((v2 + 0.19 / v1 + 0.21) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.50)))
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.abs(v2 + 0.06) + 0.55))
    data[tid] = v0
